{"tid":1865218,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"搞威脅？彭博爆：川普考慮退出WTO採購協定","createTime":"2020-02-06T05:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T13:07:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"431a360712f0b32c4b7d1d6f5580703f30e495ba","tid":1865218,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"搞威脅？彭博爆：川普考慮退出WTO採購協定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3058263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3058263&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsqHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=24e014de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3058263&h=1592dd24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3058263</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國總統川普前年曾提到要退出世界貿易組織（WTO），當時引起各界討論；有外媒引述消息人士爆料，川普有意退出WTO中的政府採購協定（GPA）。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報導，川普考慮退出WTO價值1.7兆美元的政府採購協定，消息人士透露，美國官員正在傳閱1份行政命令草案，若採購協定不按照美國的想法進行調整，美國將退出協議。<br />\n<br />\n政府採購協議是WTO訂來使政府採購過程更加透明，若美國退出採購協定，意味著英、日、南韓、加拿大和歐盟在內的成員，將失去對美國公共採購招標的優先使用權，而這些成員受制於《購買美國法》，導致多數外國企業無法競標美國政府合約。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，報導提到，美國政府此舉也符合川普的強硬風格，透過威脅退出國際公約，來增加談判影響力。目前，美國相關官員尚未對此消息進行回覆。"},{"pid":"39647522961d8e0a215bda3dc4292026afee942d","tid":1865218,"uid":199957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"431a360712f0b32c4b7d1d6f5580703f30e495ba","tid":1865218,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"搞威脅？彭博爆：川普考慮退出WTO採購協定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3058263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3058263&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsqHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=24e014de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3058263&h=1592dd24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingn